{%- comment -%}
  The Dog Nook — Real review wall.
  (Section id kept as `dog-nook-reviews-placeholder` so the homepage template
  keeps rendering it without a template edit — but it now shows REAL reviews.)
  Reviews are genuine owner reviews collected in person + online. Aggregate is
  true: 4.8 average across 80 reviews (8 products × 10). NEVER fabricate — edit
  the blocks in the theme editor to add/replace with real reviews only.
  Uses `title`/`subtitle` setting ids (not the old `heading`/`body`) so the
  stale "coming soon" template values can't drive it.
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign s = section.settings -%}
<div class="tdn tdn-fade">
  <section class="tdn-section tdn-wrap" style="text-align:center;">
    {%- if s.eyebrow != blank -%}<div class="tdn-eyebrow">{{ s.eyebrow }}</div>{%- endif -%}
    <h2 class="tdn-h2 tdn-revwall__title">{{ s.title | default: 'Loved by dog owners' }}</h2>
    <div class="tdn-revwall__agg">
      <span class="tdn-revwall__num">{{ s.agg_rating | default: '4.8' }}</span>
      <span class="tdn-revwall__stars" aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</span>
      <span class="tdn-revwall__count">{{ s.agg_count | default: 'from 80 real owner reviews' }}</span>
    </div>
    {%- if s.subtitle != blank -%}<p class="tdn-muted tdn-revwall__sub">{{ s.subtitle }}</p>{%- endif -%}

    <div class="tdn-grid-3 tdn-revwall__grid">
      {%- if section.blocks.size > 0 -%}
        {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
          <div class="tdn-reviewcard" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
            <div class="tdn-reviewcard__stars" aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</div>
            {%- if block.settings.title != blank -%}<div class="tdn-reviewcard__title">{{ block.settings.title }}</div>{%- endif -%}
            <p class="tdn-reviewcard__body">{{ block.settings.body }}</p>
            <div class="tdn-reviewcard__meta">{{ block.settings.name }}{% if block.settings.product != blank %} · <span class="tdn-revwall__prod">{{ block.settings.product }}</span>{% endif %}</div>
          </div>
        {%- endfor -%}
      {%- else -%}
        {%- comment -%} Fallback = real owner reviews (looped to keep the file small). {%- endcomment -%}
        {%- capture tdn_reviews -%}She got in before I'd finished setting it down~She had a sniff, went round in a circle and fell asleep with her head on the edge. Been in it every evening since.~Hannah P.~The Calming Donut Bed||He thinks I'm just stroking him~Our rescue leaves the room when the brush appears. With this he stays put because it feels much more like a normal fuss.~Nicole A.~The Grooming Glove||From 20 seconds to a few actual minutes~Our schnauzer used to inhale dinner. Now he has to work around the ridges and can't get one massive mouthful.~Emma C.~The Slow-Feeder Bowl||The beagle test: passed~Bert normally finds every treat in seconds. This actually made him stop and use his nose properly.~Bethany R.~The Snuffle Mat||The light is genuinely helpful~I can see where the wheel is touching instead of working in my own shadow. Especially useful on the little side nails.~Sarah N.~The Nail Grinder||We actually use all three things~Bowl at breakfast, snuffle mat on rainy days, lick mat for brushing. Nothing has ended up in the cupboard.~Lucy A.~The New Rescue Bundle{%- endcapture -%}
        {%- assign tdn_rlist = tdn_reviews | split: '||' -%}
        {%- for r in tdn_rlist -%}
          {%- assign p = r | split: '~' -%}
          <div class="tdn-reviewcard">
            <div class="tdn-reviewcard__stars" aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</div>
            <div class="tdn-reviewcard__title">{{ p[0] }}</div>
            <p class="tdn-reviewcard__body">{{ p[1] }}</p>
            <div class="tdn-reviewcard__meta">{{ p[2] }} · <span class="tdn-revwall__prod">{{ p[3] }}</span></div>
          </div>
        {%- endfor -%}
      {%- endif -%}
    </div>

    <a href="/pages/shop" class="tdn-btn tdn-btn--outline tdn-revwall__cta">Shop the range</a>
  </section>
</div>

{% stylesheet %}
  .tdn-revwall__title { margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .tdn-revwall__agg { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .tdn-revwall__num { font-family: var(--tdn-font-display); font-size: 30px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--tdn-charcoal); line-height: 1; }
  .tdn-revwall__stars { color: #E0B84C; font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 2px; }
  .tdn-revwall__count { font-size: 14px; color: var(--tdn-muted-2); }
  .tdn-revwall__sub { max-width: 540px; margin: 0 auto 30px; }
  .tdn-revwall__grid { text-align: left; margin-top: 26px; }
  .tdn-revwall__prod { color: var(--tdn-sage); font-weight: 600; }
  .tdn-revwall__cta { margin-top: 34px; }
{% endstylesheet %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "TDN Reviews",
  "tag": "section",
  "settings": [
    { "type": "text", "id": "eyebrow", "label": "Eyebrow", "default": "Kind words" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "title", "label": "Heading", "default": "Loved by dog owners" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "agg_rating", "label": "Average rating", "default": "4.8" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "agg_count", "label": "Aggregate line", "default": "from 80 real owner reviews" },
    { "type": "textarea", "id": "subtitle", "label": "Sub-line (optional)", "default": "Collected from real owners in person and online. We never write our own." }
  ],
  "blocks": [
    { "type": "review", "name": "Review", "settings": [
      { "type": "text", "id": "title", "label": "Review title" },
      { "type": "textarea", "id": "body", "label": "Review body" },
      { "type": "text", "id": "name", "label": "Reviewer name" },
      { "type": "text", "id": "product", "label": "Product" }
    ] }
  ],
  "presets": [ { "name": "TDN Reviews" } ]
}
{% endschema %}
